'''''Tyderium''''' was a [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|Lambda-class T-4a shuttle]] in service to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] personally used the shuttle with the intent of transferring [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Joser]], a [[Treason/Legends|traitor]] who wished to defect to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]], from the [[Alpha-Omega Prison]] to another facility. However, the traitorous Joser was rescued from the [[Prison/Legends|prison]] by a group of Rebels just before Vader could arrive.

